We have a new president, the rand is strengthening, and Bitcoin is back over $10,000 – things are looking up. It’s times like this, when hope outweighs despair, that you should treat yourself. Forget about saving up, just in case Zuma makes another blunder and you need to stockpile canned food – those times are over, my friend. Today is the day you buy a 7-port USB hub, not because you need one, but because you want one – and you have earned it.                                           